<LB><num value="2">Two</num> Pursuivants of Arms. 
<LB><num value="2">Two</num> Heralds. 
<LB>The <num value="2">two</num> provincial Kings of Arms <pb id="p.24" n="24"> 
<LB>The Dean of Westminter, carrying St. Edward's Crown on a cushion of cloth 
<LB>of gold. 
<LB><num value="1">First</num> Prebendary of Westminster, carrying the Orb. 
<LB><num value="2">Second</num> Prebendary, carrying the Sceptre with the Dove. 
