<num value="401">401</num>. In the library of the Inner Temple is preserved in a frame and glass a memorial, which, being but little known, is worth recording in this place :-- 
<QUOTE rend=blockquote><p><datestruct value="1661--"><year reg="1661">1661</year></datestruct>, No. <num value="3">3</num>. 
